    "The correlation between Auto-J and JudgeLM scores is 0.797.",
    "Comparing these numbers to the well-known Open LLM leaderboard from Huggingface, we see some significant differences.",
    "Although our own evaluation dataset includes some mathematical questions, it is not as math heavy as the inclusion of GSM8k at Huggingface.",
    "The biggest advancements in the overall score at Huggingface in the last months mainly came from advances in maths (see Table 6).",
    "If you look at Minotaur and Lazarus for example, they perform not too bad in ARC, HellaSwag, MMLU and TruthfulQA in comparison to the top models (~13% and 19% difference absolute), but they lack behind 62% and 58% in GSM8k."
